♪ Rounding with the little kisses
to my lips before ♪

12
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:42,210
♪ Oh, babe, I want you to be mine ♪

13
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,920
♪ Please do something ♪

14
00:00:43,940 --> 00:00:45,890
♪ To show me signs ♪

15
00:00:45,920 --> 00:00:49,680
♪ And make my world to be alright ♪

16
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:51,850
♪ Hold my hand tight ♪

17
