♪ Only tears are left ♪

741
01:00:43,930 --> 01:00:46,920
♪ Only memories remain ♪

742
01:00:46,940 --> 01:00:51,850
♪ How many more times do I have to hurt
to understand ♪

743
01:00:52,110 --> 01:00:55,090
♪ How much longer do I have to cry ♪

744
01:00:55,120 --> 01:00:59,830
♪ Before my heart tells me
it's time to let go ♪

745
01:00:59,850 --> 01:01:05,420
♪ If one day I leave ♪

746
01:01:05,570 --> 01:01:10,320
♪ You probably wouldn't feel a thing ♪

747
01:01:10,690 --> 01:01:15,440
♪ Like I never existed ♪

748
01:01:17,700 --> 01:01:21,060
♪ I must admit, it really hurts ♪

749
01:01:21,080 --> 01:01:24,390
♪ I must admit, I really miss you ♪

750
01:01:24,540 --> 01:01:26,300
♪ If there were a little love left ♪

751
