♪ My words and heart are always at odds ♪

754
01:01:34,350 --> 01:01:39,520
♪ My heart won't listen
no matter how much it hurts ♪

755
01:01:39,550 --> 01:01:40,940
♪ I must admit, I really miss you ♪

756
01:01:40,970 --> 01:01:45,010
♪ I understand it all,
but I never accepted it ♪

757
